metadata.name: Portal in the Junkyard
metadata.description:
Fully AI-generated, advanced oil paintings. Every artwork has its own story. 1/1 collection also includes pop art and modern art references.

"Portal in the Junkyard" 

A mysterious portal that opens in a junkyard of technology waste in a CyberPunk, futuristic world.

Back to the Future, Terminator, Ready Player One, etc. references were used for this AI dream.
